Description:
   Cloak:elements is the Wizard's signature remort cloak. It surrounds the
   caster in a crackling aura of raw elemental power. When the caster takes
   non-physical (spell) damage, the cloak lashes back and reflects 15% of the
   incoming damage at the attacker as water-element damage.

   The reflected damage bypasses reflection and absorption effects (it carries
   NO_REFLECT and NO_ABSORB flags). The cloak only triggers against non-
   physical damage that does not already have NO_REFLECT or NO_ABSORB set --
   physical attacks do not activate it.

   For a similar effect against physical damage, see cloak:flaming (Sorcerer).

   Duration scales with pseudo-level (pseudo_level / 8 rounds).
